snippet.title: Beto vs Gun-Rights Lady & Brandt Jean Forgives Amber Guyer | Michael Anderson & Matt Travis
snippet.description:
Beto vs Gun-Rights Lady & Brandt Jean Forgives Amber Guyer | Liberty Talks EP. 54 with Michael Anderson & Matt Travis

Michael Anderson and Matt Travis discuss Beto being confronted by a Gun-Rights Lady at his Aurora, CO & Brandt Jean Forgiveing Amber Guyer - a cop convicted of murdering his brother.
